\f1\b0 : Roy, in the Positioning section of BJJ201, you show an example of countering the armbar by placing your head over top of Mr. Dean's head. You also are jamming your knees into Mr. Dean's head so that he can't roll to his stomach to finish the armbar. Here are my two questions:\
