Question: 
\f2\fs25 Roy, Do you think the guard in no gi is getting harder and harder to play , and a top game is becoming more of preference? When i go with the stiffer muscley base driven elbows tucked in guys, I feel a tad helpless or confused as to what may nullify these rigid players.
\f1\fs24 \
\
